A '''Talmog''' was an [[Alcohol/Legends|alcoholic]] drink common during the Imperial era. It consisted of one part spiced [[ethanol]] and one part [[Lyme's rose juice]]. It was reportedly popular in a sunless, centerless system and was known for creating a burning feeling when consumed.

[[Lando Calrissian/Legends|Lando Calrissian]] hated them, but would order one while playing [[Sabacc/Legends|sabacc]] so he would not overdrink and muddle his wits.

